{
  "id": "db-pool-001",
  "version": 1,
  "title": "DB プールが呼吸できない夜",
  "difficulty": "intermediate",
  "difficultyScore": 230,
  "timeLimitMinutes": 10,
  "service": {
    "name": "やまびこ API",
    "healthUrl": "http://localhost:8080/health"
  },
  "briefing": [
    "DB 接続プールが飽和すると、API は新しい接続を拒否されて 5xx を返し始める。",
    "誰が接続を握っているのか。メトリクスの DB Conn と fake-db の統計から犯人を探す。",
    "再起動だけでは直らない障害もある。"
  ],
  "startup": [
    {
      "id": "api",
      "command": "PORT=8080 node /workspace/services/yamabiko-api/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 8080
    },
    {
      "id": "fake-db",
      "command": "node /workspace/services/fake-db/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 15432
    }
  ],
  "topology": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "user",
        "label": "ユーザー",
        "kind": "external"
      },
      {
        "id": "api",
        "label": "やまびこ API",
        "kind": "service",
        "processId": "api"
      },
      {
        "id": "fake-db",
        "label": "疑似データベース",
        "kind": "datastore",
        "processId": "fake-db"
      },
      {
        "id": "report-batch",
        "label": "月次レポートバッチ",
        "kind": "batch"
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "from": "user",
        "to": "api"
      },
      {
        "from": "api",
        "to": "fake-db"
      },
      {
        "from": "report-batch",
        "to": "fake-db"
      }
    ]
  },
  "triggers": [
    {
      "id": "pool-exhaust",
      "atMs": 30000,
      "type": "db_pool_exhaust",
      "params": {
        "connections": 40
      }
    }
  ],
  "alerts": [
    {
      "id": "db-pool",
      "atMs": 60000,
      "severity": "critical",
      "message": "DB connection pool exhausted",
      "source": "monitor"
    },
    {
      "id": "api-5xx",
      "atMs": 75000,
      "severity": "critical",
      "message": "HTTP 5xx rate is above threshold",
      "source": "scenario"
    }
  ],
  "successConditions": [
    {
      "type": "http_status",
      "url": "http://localhost:8080/health",
      "status": 200
    },
    {
      "type": "process_running",
      "processId": "api"
    },
    {
      "type": "process_running",
      "processId": "fake-db"
    }
  ],
  "runbooks": [
    {
      "id": "runbook.db-pool",
      "title": "DB 接続飽和の初動",
      "body": "1. 監視の DB Conn が上限(40)に張り付いていないか確認する\n2. fake-db の統計で「どのアプリが」接続を握っているか見る\n   (統計は /workspace/run/fake-db-stats.json に出ている)\n3. 接続を握っているプロセスを特定して止める(ps / kill)\n4. DB を再起動しても、犯人が生きていればすぐ再発する\n5. curl localhost:8080/health で復旧確認する"
    }
  ],
  "chatMessages": [
    {
      "id": "dba",
      "atMs": 70000,
      "from": "DBA",
      "body": "プールサイズいじった？上限は 40 のはずだけど。"
    },
    {
      "id": "senpai",
      "atMs": 130000,
      "from": "先輩(仮眠中)",
      "body": "ん…月次レポートのバッチ、今夜だったかも…zzz"
    }
  ],
  "navigationSteps": [
    {
      "id": "nav-db-conn",
      "atMs": 0,
      "hint": "DB Conn メトリクスが上限に張り付いていないか見る",
      "panel": "metrics"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-stats",
      "atMs": 40000,
      "hint": "fake-db の統計で接続元の内訳を確認する",
      "panel": "terminal",
      "suggestedCommand": "cat /workspace/run/fake-db-stats.json"
    }
  ]
}
